just slide it over here.

14:57.314 --> 14:59.415
[ALL LAUGHING]

14:59.417 --> 15:01.784
[ALL CHEERING]

15:01.786 --> 15:04.587
So Brandon, I hear
you're killing it in school.

15:04.589 --> 15:07.790
- Tested in the top one percent.
- No, he tested in the top

15:07.792 --> 15:09.358
one tenth of one percent.

15:09.360 --> 15:11.861
