is talking about him.

15:11.863 --> 15:13.930
He's our little super genius.

15:13.932 --> 15:15.731
MAN:
So a special guy

15:15.733 --> 15:18.066
deserves a very special present.

15:18.068 --> 15:23.071
This is from me
and your Aunt Merilee.

15:23.073 --> 15:25.140
MERILEE:
Go ahead, open it.

15:25.142 --> 15:28.145
I shot my first buck
with that very same model.

15:29.747 --> 15:32.782
Whoa, no, no, no.
No guns.

15:32.784 --> 15:34.884
- We talked about this, Tori.
- I know...

15:34.886 --> 15:36.752
Come on, he's still
just a kid.

15:36.754 --> 15:38.086
I'm 12 years old.

15:38.088 --> 15:40.190
I know, exactly,
you're still a child.

15:41.359 --> 15:42.792
Give it to me.

15:42.794 --> 15:45.126
I'm sorry, what did
you just say to me?

15:45.128 --> 15:47.565
- I said, "give it to me."
