15:48.800 --> 15:49.799
Brandon.

15:49.801 --> 15:51.434
Okay, we're done here.

15:51.436 --> 15:54.637
We're not having ice cream.
Thank you. Let's go.

15:54.639 --> 15:56.539
Brandon, let's go.
Brandon!

15:56.541 --> 15:58.273
- [ELECTRONICS BEEPING]
- Up now.

15:58.275 --> 16:00.008
Brandon...

16:00.010 --> 16:01.346
