16:08.419 --> 16:10.353
Okay... sorry.

16:10.355 --> 16:12.254
- Don't worry about.
- So sorry.

16:12.256 --> 16:14.490
TORI:
Nope. Yep, bye.

16:14.492 --> 16:15.960
MERILEE:
I love you guys!

16:17.862 --> 16:19.662
Babe, I told you.

16:19.664 --> 16:21.330
You sure you want kids?

16:21.332 --> 16:23.164
I just don't get
that kid.

16:23.166 --> 16:25.935
